text: San Carlo is a village in Tuscany, central Italy, administratively a frazione of the comune of San Vincenzo, province of Livorno. At the time of the 2011 census its population was 256. The village is about 62 km from Livorno and 5 km from San Vincenzo. == External links == * Category:Frazioni of the Province of Livorno
title: San Carlo, San Vincenzo
